    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul class="ingredients">
      <li>250g lady finger (okra)</li>
      <li>2 tbsp oil</li>
      <li>1 onion, sliced</li>
      <li>1/2 tsp turmeric</li>
      <li>1 tsp red chili powder</li>
      <li>Salt to taste</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Instructions</h2>
    <button onclick="toggleInstructions()">Show/Hide Steps</button>
    <div class="instructions" id="steps">
      <p>1. Wash and dry the lady fingers. Cut into small pieces.</p>
      <p>2. Heat oil in a pan. Add onions and sautÃ©.</p>
      <p>3. Add chopped lady finger and spices.</p>
      <p>4. Cook on medium heat until crispy. Serve hot.</p>
